author: mischnic
message:
Turbopack: add webpack scope-hoisting tests (#79457)

Add them already, they should pass even without scope hoisting.

files.patch:
@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+# Goes through all subfolders of $folder and moves all files into a new "input" subdirectory
+
+
+folder=scope-hoisting
+
+set -e
+shopt -s extglob
+
+for f in "$folder"/*; do
+  mkdir -p "$f/input"
+  mv "$f"/!(input) "$f"/input
+done

+function f(test = test2, { test2: t2 } = { test2 }, { t3 = test3 } = {}) {
+  return [test, t2, t3]
+}
+
+export default {
+  obj,
+  nested,
+  test,
+  test2,
+  test3,
+  test4,
+  f: f(),
+}
